      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical option for a buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The engine is functional and the car is drivable, though it does show its age with some minor leaks and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. It is a reliable runner for daily commutes but will eventually require some maintenance to keep it in peak operating form.",
