      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
