    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride of ownership. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage, it presents beautifully with a deep, glossy finish. While there are a few minor, nearly imperceptible stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use, the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the cabin retains its premium feel; the leather seats are supple and show minimal wear, and the interior has never been smoked in. Every feature, from the responsive touchscreen interface to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule with synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and I have the full service history available for your review. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With recent tire replacements and a fresh brake service, this car is turn-key and ready for its next journey.",
